The '''Corporeal Beast''', often referred to simply as '''Corp''', is a large monster residing in its [[Corporeal Beast's Lair|lair]], accessed via [[games necklace]] or an entrance in level 21 [[Wilderness]]. Due to its very high combat stats, it is often fought by groups of players. Unlike its ''RuneScape 3'' counterpart, it has no quest requirements to access.

The Corporeal Beast is the only monster to drop the [[spirit shield]], as well as the [[holy elixir]] and [[arcane sigil|arcane]], [[elysian sigil|elysian]], and [[spectral sigil|spectral]] sigils, used to enhance the shield. In addition to its sigil drops, the Corporeal Beast has many other valuable drops. Unlike some other group bosses, only the player who dealt the most damage will receive kill credit and loot.

Players can pay 200,000 coins to open a group instance for their [[chat-channel]] via the [[private portal]], excluding [[Ironman Mode|ironmen]].

